4. Application Name: 
    Loco-Notion
5. Application Description:
    An app for organizing thoughts. It would have a navbar with different sections, like a brain dump section which lets you quickly write something (potentially using voice-to-text) and stores it in a database. There would also be a goals section/to do section that could send you reminders. Additionally, there would be a study mode where academic tasks are shown one at a time to keep you focused on each individual task.
6. Audience:
    People with ADHD, people with disorganized thoughts, type B people.
7. Vision Statement:
    For type B people, Who need a better way to organize and remember their thoughts. The Loco-Notion software is a note writing app/organizer that lets you tag your notes to more effectively sort through them. Unlike typical notes apps, our product lets you filter by self-created tags to better manage your thoughts.
